          <div class="experience-company">Mindvalley</div>
          <div class="experience-role">Tech Lead</div>
          <div class="experience-period">2019 - 2021</div>
          <div class="experience-description">
            <p>Led team of 5 engineers building content discovery experience for 300K+ Monthly Active Users. Transformed team from "treading water" to "repaying debt" state, improving technical health.</p>
